{"tid":2344382,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"保安局接獲台山核電站通報柴油機上周五一度故障停運","createTime":"2020-12-28T16:22:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-29T03:49:08.000Z","uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e8dcf695083981a5c8789c55e13247489c711262","tid":2344382,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T16:22:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1567527-20201228.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1567527-20201228.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=vFDcqKLMx6N8Vlwxc9Uzx2g5BW3O7pEdz%2F%2BecHjXtrw%3D&h=9190618c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1567527-20201228.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=a7577b79\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1567527-20201228.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n保安局表示，台山核電合營有限公司在網站通報一則有關台山核電站的運行事件，指核電站2號機組在上星期五按計劃開展電站柴油機定期試驗期間，柴油機因勵磁設備故障停運，工作人員立即按程序開展恢復操作，柴油機之後恢復正常。根據國際核事件分級表以及核安全法規，事件確定為0級偏差事件，對機組安全運行、員工健康、周邊公眾和環境沒有影響。<br />\n<br />\n發言人表示，過程中機組始終處於安全運行狀態，台山核電站於事發後將情況報告核安全監管單位，進行故障原因分析及處理，並在電站內部開展經驗反饋。"},{"pid":"0de01f6d5b2629b0a6f2f8479f45d2d0ef7ba445","tid":2344382,"uid":24730,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T16:42:32.000Z","msg":"係咪廣東停電嗰日？"},{"pid":"6ca4b8753a6c8eb4c0490de751912e7d1b720652","tid":2344382,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T16:45:22.000Z","msg":"隔3日先講？"},{"pid":"3b4def5facc22a8935ee38b19965e79e6eaa8739","tid":2344382,"uid":264245,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T00:51:05.000Z","msg":"咁咪係試過降唔温？"},{"pid":"a9afe2cfc163f47e22bbd015710a6d71c56e1e53","tid":2344382,"uid":7323,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"6ca4b8753a6c8eb4c0490de751912e7d1b720652","tid":2344382,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T16:45:22